text.tspan: When you take an action that risk failure
or opposition, role with the relevant stat.
On a 10+, you succeed at your goal, and the
MC may reward you accordingly. On a 7-9,
the MC will offer you a bargain or cost. If
you agree, you succeed (and the MC will
still reward you). Below that, you fail.
You may help or hinder both PCs and
NPCs. Roll your Leverage stat for that
person. On a 10+ for a PC, add or subtract
2 to their roll. On a 7-9, the MC will name
a cost to do so. For an NPC, rather than
